data.description:
PRICE JUST REDUCED ANOTHER 10K! SELLER SAYS BRING OFFERS!
POOL HOME IN THE CENTRALLY LOCATED POPULAR PARKWAY MEADOWS NEIGHBORHOOD. 3 Bedroom 2 bath is completely fenced giving total swimming privacy and Florida room seclusion. Separate Family room, Living Room and dining room. Breakfast nook. 
UPGRADED ROLEX SHUTTERS COMPLETELY WRAPS AROUND ENTIRE HOUSE. JUST PRESS A BUTTON FOR COMPLETE HOUSE PROTECTION INCLUDING THE ENTIRE FLORIDA ROOM! Generator will do the  house with the transfer switch in the garage! This very  Cozy home offers Tile  and wood floors with no carpet! Tile also in the huge Florida Room!  2nd Bathroom has an upgraded walk in Jacuzzi tub to enjoy. Wonderful location within minutes from Publix, Walmart, eateries, Wickham Park, the beach and 95. Easy in and out off Parkway Drive.
